Fall 1976
Braniff gets you there
with Flying Colors

BRANIFF
SERVICE
HIGHLIGHTS
• CHICAGO — Daily flights to Dallas-Fort Worth every hour on the
hour from 9 AM to 6 PM - eight are non-stop. Five non-stops
to Houston. Non-stop flight to Oklahoma City at 6:55 PM.
• DALLAS-FORT WORTH - New York service includes 10 non-
stops to New York-Newark — four to LaGuardia, four to Newark
and two to Kennedy. Every hour to Chicago from 8:20 AM to
• 6:20 PM. Eight flights to Washington, D.C. — six one-stops to
National Airport and two non-stops to Dulles. The only daily
non-stops to Miami* plus four non-stops daily to Tampa-St.
Petersburg, 2 to Fort Lauderdale. Honolulu 747 non-stop
departs daily at 1:15 PM.
• DENVER — Four flights daily to Atlanta... all thru-flights. Non-
stops to Memphis and Oklahoma City. Every-hour-on-the-hour
to Dallas-Fort Worth every weekday. The only thru-service to
all three Florida cities - Tampa, Fort Lauderdale and Miami.
• HOUSTON - Evening service to Kansas City with direct
connections from Kansas City to Minneapolis-St. Paul and
Detroit. Four non-stops to Chicago. Every-hour-on-the-hour
service to Dallas-Fort Worth. Acapulco flights twice daily.
• KANSAS CITY - Evening service to Chicago leaving at 9:35 PM
makes a total of eight non-stops. Evening non-stop flight to
Minneapolis-St. Paul departing at 9:30 PM. Five thru-flights to
Houston including non-stops at 8:45 AM and 6:25 PM. Nine
non-stops to Dallas-Fort Worth.
• MINNEAPOLIS-ST. PAUL - Evening non-stop flight to Des Moines
with thru-service to Kansas City and Dallas-Fort Worth. Ten
• NEW OR EARS - musions sis every business day
to Dallas-Fort Worth - four from LaGuardia, four from Newark and
two from Kennedy. Five one-stops to Houston weekdays and six
thru flights to San Antonio.
• OKLAHOMA CITY — Afternoon non-stop to Chicago leaving at
5.20 PM. Two non-stops daily to Denver. Seven flights to Dallas-
Fort Worth including new evening flight departing at 9:10 PM.
• TULSA — Afternoon service to Kansas City and Des Moines,
departing at 6:25 PM provides additional thru-service to
Minneapolis-St. Paul.
Check our schedule for these and other Braniff flights throughout
the U.S. Mainland, Hawaii, Mexico and South America. Then for
reservations call your travel professional or Braniff International.
*Effective September 8, 1976
